    "name": "Everton Nelson",
    "profile": "Violinist. Having toured extensively throughout the world with the Ryuichi Sakamoto Trio and band, Everton is now much in demand as a session musician. With 20 years of experience under his belt he has recorded with some of the world’s leading recording artists including: Adele, Sam Smith, Ed Sheeran, Amy Winehouse, Sade, Peter Gabriel, Mary J Blige, Sting, Gregory Porter, Stevie Wonder, Alicia Keyes, Florence and the Machine and Joni Mitchell.\r\n\r\nAs an orchestral leader Everton has lead movie soundtrack recordings for film composers including:\r\nCarter Burwell (Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri, Wonderstruck, The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part 1 & 2, Seven Psychopaths)\r\nDanny Elfman ( Alice Through the Looking Glass, Hitchcock)\r\nHenry Jackman (Kingsman: The Golden Circle, Captain America, Puss in Boots)\r\nMarc Streitenfeld (Prometheus)\r\nHeitor Pereira (Angry Birds)\r\nRamin Djawadi (The Great Wall, Warcraft, Safe House)\r\nSteven Price (Gravity, Attack the Block)\r\nAlberto Inglesi",
